Package com.ss4group8

Class Mark

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ss4group8.Mark
  • public class Mark
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a student mark record associated with one student and a course. Both students and courses can have multiple student mark record, but cannot be duplicate.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ma Xiao, Fu Mengyan, Kevin Steven Kihata, Ng Chen Ee Kenneth, Ian Tan Yi
